<p><strong>Step 1: List your core topics.</strong> Identify 5 to 10 broad topics your business covers. For Stacc, these include blog SEO, local SEO, content automation, and SEO tools.</p>
<p><strong>Step 2: Generate keywords for each stage.</strong></p>
