<p><strong>Step 3: Check search volume and intent.</strong></p>
<p>Run each keyword through <a href="/glossary/keyword-research/">keyword research</a> tools. Verify the intent by searching Google and examining the top results. If the SERP shows guides, the keyword is TOFU. If it shows product pages, the keyword is BOFU.</p>
<p><strong>Step 4: Map keywords to existing or planned content.</strong></p>
<p>Create a spreadsheet with columns for: keyword, search volume, intent type, funnel stage, target URL, and status (published/planned).</p>
<p><strong>Step 5: Identify gaps.</strong></p>
<p>Most businesses discover they have plenty of TOFU content and almost no MOFU or BOFU content. Fill the gaps. MOFU and BOFU content drives revenue directly.</p>
